Testing Extensions
---------------
Visual Studio Code supports running and debugging tests for your extension. 

These tests will run inside a special instance of VS Code named the Extension Development Host, and have full access to the VS Code API. 


https://code.visualstudio.com/api/working-with-extensions/testing-extension
https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-extension-samples/tree/master/helloworld-test-sample
https://vscode-docs.readthedocs.io/en/stable/extensions/testing-extensions/




